He can control people's memories
at will.

37
00:02:30,719 --> 00:02:32,020
How did you give orders
to your accomplice?

38
00:02:33,289 --> 00:02:34,289
Read my memory.

39
00:02:34,789 --> 00:02:36,259
- Do you mean it?
- Of course.

40
00:02:37,199 --> 00:02:40,060
Because the victims
have been chosen.

41
00:02:40,469 --> 00:02:42,930
The last one will die
before the end of the month...

42
00:02:44,169 --> 00:02:46,039
because you have touched them.

43
00:02:50,009 --> 00:02:51,439
What did you see in his memories?

44
00:02:51,580 --> 00:02:53,310
- The secret passage.
- Don't you find it strange?

45
00:02:53,509 --> 00:02:57,080
Why would such a meticulous guy
leave traces of the water pump?

46
00:02:57,180 --> 00:02:58,280
Just get to the point.

47
00:02:58,650 --> 00:02:59,650
The accomplice.

48
00:02:59,979 --> 00:03:02,120
Was the secret passage made
in order to hide his accomplice?

49
00:03:02,819 --> 00:03:03,889
Yoon Hee Tae.

50
