Yoon Hee Tae owns dozens of
properties under borrowed names,

51
00:03:06,719 --> 00:03:07,930
and they're all located
in secluded areas.

52
00:03:07,930 --> 00:03:13,500
(Previously on Memorist)

53
00:03:13,530 --> 00:03:14,930
I didn't know you'd make it here.

54
00:03:15,669 --> 00:03:18,639
Getting rid of you two
and getting on a boat...

55
00:03:18,639 --> 00:03:20,370
will take me only three minutes.

56
00:03:21,569 --> 00:03:23,370
1 minute 30 seconds.

57
00:03:23,840 --> 00:03:24,939
He has a knife!

58
00:03:27,210 --> 00:03:28,310
You failed.

59
00:03:29,050 --> 00:03:30,819
The kid and his mom are both safe.

60
00:03:31,020 --> 00:03:32,050
What?

61
00:03:32,520 --> 00:03:33,819
Something's not right.

62
00:03:34,419 --> 00:03:35,490
No...

63
00:03:37,419 --> 00:03:38,460
No.

